===Noun===
'''pastry''' (''plural:'' '''[[pastries]]''')

# a [[baked]] food group which contains items made from [[flour]] and fat pastes such as pie crust; also [[tart]]s, [[bear claw]]s, [[napolean]]s, [[puff pastries]], etc.

